shortFormVideos.title: Confronting Chaos
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Ps. Monte teaches us our world is filled with chaos, but Jesus Is the Peace Who goes beyond our wildest expectation!

shortFormVideos.title: Radical Belief
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Jesus listed some very specific evidence of true belief. The question we should ask ourselves is do we truly trust Him, do we really rely on Him, and are we willing to obey Him?

shortFormVideos.title: Radical Evidence
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Demons are determined to take your Treasure, Life, and to create chaos in your world. But the Name of Jesus Is the highest Authority over everything that comes against us and in Him we have Authority.

shortFormVideos.title: Radical Evidence Pt. 2
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: There's real Evidence of being a believer in Jesus. An aspect of this Evidence are New Languages that Jesus will speak through you. Let's unpack what happens when we receive the Gift of the Holy Ghost

shortFormVideos.title: RADICAL EVIDENCE - Snakes and Poison
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: We all come under attack in our lives. In this sermon, Pastor Monte teaches us how to recognize snakes and poison the enemy will use to distract us, or even kill us Spiritually.

shortFormVideos.title: RADICAL EVIDENCE - Hands of Restoration
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: If we truly believe, through the Authority of His Identity, we have the Authority to place our hands on sick people and they will be well.

shortFormVideos.title: RADICAL ACTION - Living Belief
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Ps. Monte teaches us that belief in Jesus isn't just an idea--GOD is calling every believer to action, and to LIVE out their belief in ACTION!

shortFormVideos.title: RADICAL ACTION - Equipped For Action
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Jesus provides all the Equipment we need to serve other believers and to shine His Light and Love to the lost. Pastor Monte unpacks 1 Corinthians 12, diving into the 9 Primary Spiritual Gifts.

shortFormVideos.title: RADICAL ACTION - Community Action
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Ps. Chris Landeche teaches us that Jesus uses our relationships with other people to connect them with His Presence.

shortFormVideos.title: RADICAL ACTION - GOD In Action
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: GOD displays His Action throughout His Word. Through history we see His mighty Arm and powerful Hand at work in our story. We see His Identity through the work of His Finger.

shortFormVideos.title: RADICAL ACTION - GOD In Action Pt. 2
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Jesus wants to reveal Himself in you, but first you have to know Who He Is.

shortFormVideos.title: RADICAL - THE FINISHED WORK - Greater Things
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Jesus has already finished the work, but He's calling you to Greater Things!

shortFormVideos.title: RADICAL Communion
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Communion is more than a religious ceremony, it's a celebration of His Finished Work, and our freedom from sin.

shortFormVideos.title: Creation | The Beginning
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Creation didn't just happen... it wasn't random... it Exposes GOD's Plan to bring you to Himself.

shortFormVideos.title: Creation | From Chaos to Light
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: No matter what you're going through, Jesus Is there in your circumstance!

shortFormVideos.title: Creation | Environments
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Jesus is EVERYTHING you'll ever need to accomplish EVERYTHING he designed you to do and to be.

shortFormVideos.title: Creation | Exceedingly TOV
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: GOD fashioned us in HIS Image, and in HIS Likeness!

shortFormVideos.title: Creation | Rest
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Because GOD finished his work on the seventh day and rested, we can follow His example!

shortFormVideos.title: The Fall | Eve & Adam
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Jesus will never abandon you… no matter what you think about Him. In fact, in the middle of your failures you’ll see Him clearly Exposed, ready to cover every sin with His Identity!

shortFormVideos.title: The Fall | Cain's Fall
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: No matter how far you've stumbled, Jesus will never abandon you, and He'll never stop reaching for you.

shortFormVideos.title: The Fall | Breath Of Life
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Jesus wants to give you the Breath of Life!

shortFormVideos.title: The Fall | Lamech's Fall
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Did you know our choices directly impact the Legacy we leave? The good thing is, even in our stumblings, Jesus is still there!

shortFormVideos.title: RESCUE | Calling Noah
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: No matter what you're facing, no matter what surrounds you, Jesus has already provided Rescue!

shortFormVideos.title: RESCUE | Finding Favor
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Our world can seem chaotic, but in the midst of our chaos Jesus reveals Himself and provides us Rescue.

shortFormVideos.title: RESCUE | Walking Legacy
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Our story may not always be what we want it to be, but if we make ourselves available to God He can use it for amazing things!

shortFormVideos.title: RESCUE | Rescue Provided
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Jesus has already provided EVERYTHING you need for the Rescue He planned for you before the beginning!

shortFormVideos.title: RESCUE | Preparing Rescue
shortFormVideos.shortDescription: Have you ever wondered why your relationship with Jesus can sometimes feel like you've hit a brick wall? Here's the good news... Jesus has already prepared everything you need to enter His Rescue!
